PrecisAuthority for VIA RAIL CANADA INC. to lease, for a period of 50 years, its railway station in TROIS-RIVIÈRES (Quebec), a designated heritage railway station, to the MUNICIPALITÉ RÉGIONALE DU COMTÉ DE FRANCHEVILLE, and to subsequently make renovations to construct offices.
